===Etymology===
From {{suffix|antinomian|ism|lang=en}}, coined by {{w|Martin Luther}}, notably used in his ''Against the Antinomians'' (1539).

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/æntiˈnoʊmi.ənɪzəm/|lang=en}}
